  "description": {
    "zh": "接下来的任务会变得更加复杂，请做好准备。这里不仅有本地帮派和土匪，还有进口帮派和邪教徒在四处游荡，威胁着整个区域的安全。\n\n你需要格外小心，尤其是大型建筑工地附近，那里是这些渣滓的聚集地。希望你已经准备好迎接这些挑战了。",
    "en": "Now this is gonna be even more complicated so prepare. A bunch of local gangs and bandits roam that place, but not just them, the imports and cultists are there too and haunt the place...\n\nYou need to be extremely careful around the big construction site, it's a hot spot for this kind of scum. I hope you are ready for that."
  },
